text: Chukadytamak () is a rural locality (a selo) in Karamaly-Gubeyevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 398 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 41 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Karamaly-Gubeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Chukadytamak
